    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality FD3S RX-7, featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine with factory-spec compression and a perfectly synchronized sequential twin-turbocharger setup. This specimen retains its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring the precise turn-in and 50/50 weight distribution the chassis is celebrated for. The five-speed manual gearbox exhibits crisp gate engagement with zero synchro hesitation. Meticulously maintained, the engine bay features supple vacuum lines and an upgraded aluminum radiator for superior thermal management. All original VIN tags are present on factory body panels, confirming an accident-free provenance. This is a benchmark example of JDM engineering, optimized for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and unadulterated performance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Garage kept. Full service history included. Inspect in person.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
