    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate-controlled seating, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never been exposed to inclement weather. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this is arguably the finest example currently available on the market.",
