      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty\u2014it is honestly in absolute mint condition! It feels just like it rolled off the lot yesterday, with that fresh car smell and a ride that's as smooth as silk. I've taken such good care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It\u2019s a total dream to drive, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to fall in love with it the moment you get behind the wheel. Come take a look!",
